# Frozen Inventory Git Ignore Information

This .gitignore file is configured for the Frozen Inventory Rails application.

## Key Files Being Ignored (Security & Performance):

### Database Files
- *.sqlite3, *.sqlite3-*, *.db (development databases)
- /storage/* (SQLite database storage)

### Secrets & Configuration
- .env* files (environment variables with secrets)
- /config/master.key (Rails encrypted credentials key)
- /config/credentials/*.key (additional credential keys)
- /.kamal/secrets* (deployment secrets)

### Logs & Temporary Files
- /log/* (application logs)
- /tmp/* (temporary files and caches)

### System & IDE Files
- .DS_Store (macOS), Thumbs.db (Windows)
- .vscode/, .idea/, *.swp (IDE configuration)

### Dependencies & Assets
- /node_modules (if using Node.js)
- /public/assets (compiled assets)
- /vendor/bundle (bundled gems)

## Files Being Tracked:
- Application source code (app/, config/, lib/)
- Gemfile & Gemfile.lock (dependency definitions)
- Database migrations (db/migrate/)
- Tests (test/)
- Documentation (README.md)
- Configuration templates (without secrets)